 RA8875 communication, connect:
 
   TFTM070(40 pin)   Arduino UNO pin    Description
    1,2                                 GND
    3,4                                 VCC
    5                10                 SPI SELECT
    6                ICSP_MISO          SDO / SPI_MISO
    7                ICSP_MOSI          SDI / SPI_MOSI
    8                ICSP_SCK           CLK                
    9                NC
   10                3                  INTERRUPT

   12 (why?)         9              RESET
